　　“Do you remrmber ?  When  you  were sixteen…seventeen…looking ahead…Next couple of years ,I would be great. Just knew it. Idon't feel like that any more.”
　　“啊？”
　　他见我有听没有懂，满脸问号的样子，山西终于抿嘴一笑。然后，似乎真把我视为笨蛋地说了句“笨～～蛋”。
